### Can you introduce yourself (name, location, age, etc..)?
Hi my name is melvin. i live in Connecticut .

### How did you get interested in programming?

I saw the ad on youtube. I always had love for Computers,but on 
the hardware side. 


### When did you start learning to code?
I took a class in high school , but i never stuck 
with it.



### Where do you learn new skills?

I learn my new skills on Codingphase and also Udemy.

### What do you love the most about programming?

I love the creativity and the flexibilities
coding brings.

### What do you hate about programming?

I have to think hard about this.  

### Are you currently working as a developer?

No working on my skills at codingphase.com and Udemy.

### What's your favorite stack or type of applications?

I am like working with css and Html and i also like javascript,
java, react,ruby.

### What's a technology or language or skill you wish to learn in the future?

 I want to learn aws also DevOps and kotlin.

### Where do you see yourself in 5 years?

I want to be working as a developer or a business owner.

### If you were to go back into time and give yourself an advice to make it easier to learn to code what would you say?

I would have focused on coding early.
